  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">SRM - boot</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">On real SRM, <text styleclass="Code Example">boot</text> bootstraps the operating system using <text styleclass="Code Example">bootdef_dev</text> and <text styleclass="Code Example">boot_osflags</text>. On EmulatR, OS bootstrap is not yet implemented -- the console reaches <text styleclass="Code Example">&gt;&gt;&gt;</text> and halts. The related <text styleclass="Code Example">auto_action</text> variable supports HALT (the default and only fully implemented action); BOOT and RESTART are planned.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
